{"tid":2172814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】特朗普指「不再依賴中國」，劉鶴與美貿易代表Lighthizer及財長Mnuchin通話","createTime":"2020-08-25T01:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T03:33:58.000Z","uid":48040,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c5260d9d6edf320e7b088a03a0b050711ecf6252","tid":2172814,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:07:47.000Z","msg":"8月25日上午，中共中央政治局委員、國務院副總理、中美全面經濟對話中方牽頭人劉鶴應約與美國貿易代表Lighthizer、財長Mnuchin通話。雙方就加强两國宏觀經濟政策協調、中美第一階段經貿協議落實等問題進行了具有建設性的對話。雙方同意創造條件和氛圍，繼續推動中美第一階段經貿協議落實。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-08/25/c_1126408888.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fworld%2F2020-08%2F25%2Fc_1126408888.htm&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=70613108\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2020-08/25/c_1126408888.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n競選連任陣營在星期天（2020年8月23日）宣布的特朗普總統第二任期施政綱領中列出了在經濟、教育、外交政策與國防等十大領域的施政重點。施政綱領將&ldquo;終止對中國的依賴&rdquo;排在十大重點施政領域的第三位。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-campaign-china-top-agenda-20200824/5555343.html?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=dlvr.it\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Ftrump-campaign-china-top-agenda-20200824%2F5555343.html%3Futm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Ddlvr.it&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=1b0f3923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-campaign-china-top-agenda-20200824/5555343.html?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=dlvr.it</a>"},{"pid":"52ce42772a9e4dd59fe4b7a912fe8900c1ed46d7","tid":2172814,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ca10ae0ba6476e4968aada59560078bc7c7117",